column12:
Group Leader to call chauffeur when all passengers and let chauffeur know when they are walking to the charter bus lot. 

Proceed to baggage claim. Take escalator, stairs or elevator to skybridge #6 and cross to parking garage. 
Take the BLUE elevators to Level One and follow the signs to holding area for cruise ships and charter buses. 
There is a 5-10 minute wait for your shuttle to arrive once driver has been called (if not done ahead of time). 
If you do not have driver name & number call dispatch at (206) 233-9233. 
You may also dial 55 from any courtesy phone to speak with airport customer service to let them know you are looking for your chartered shuttle for assistance from airport staff.
